  (text "PHOTONIC ENGINE BLOCK\n8ch TFLN Modulator + DFB Laser Array\nWavelength: 1550nm C-band\nModulation: 200G PAM4 per lane" (at 101.6 44.45 0) (effects (font (size 2.0 2.0)) (justify left)))
  (text "CLOCK & BIAS CONTROL\nSi5395A: jitter < 100 fs RMS\nAD5684R: quad 12-bit bias DAC\nI2C addr: 0x68 (clk), 0x0C (DAC)" (at 228.6 44.45 0) (effects (font (size 2.0 2.0)) (justify left)))
  (text "POWER MANAGEMENT\n12V PCIe -> 3.3V (TPS54360 buck, 3A)\n3.3V -> 1.8V (TPS7A2018 LDO, 200mA)\nTotal board power: ~25W" (at 304.8 44.45 0) (effects (font (size 2.0 2.0)) (justify left)))
  (text "LASER DRIVER & TEC\nMAX3669: 4ch laser driver, 25 Gbps/ch\nMPT5000: TEC loop, +/-3A\nTemp setpoint: 25 deg C +/- 0.01 deg C" (at 55.88 170.18 0) (effects (font (size 2.0 2.0)) (justify left)))
  (text "BOARD SPECIFICATIONS\nAggregate bandwidth: 1.6 Tbps (8 x 200G)\nForm factor: PCIe half-height, 168 x 100 mm\nInterface: PCIe Gen 6.0 x16, OSFP host-side\nOptical front-end: MPO-24\nLayer count: 10\nImpedance: 50 ohm SE, 100 ohm differential\nSubstrate: Megtron-7 low-loss (Dk 3.3, Df 0.002 @ 10 GHz)" (at 25.4 254.0 0) (effects (font (size 2.0 2.0)) (justify left)))

